[
    {
        "idx": 0,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "Ali, Sara, Omar, and Lina were walking home after school when the sky suddenly grew dark. The wind moved through the trees, and the street became unusually quiet. Ali stopped and said,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 1,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "Did you hear that?",
        "speaker": "Ali",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "voice_id": "CwhRBWXzGAHq8TQ4Fs17"
    },
    {
        "idx": 2,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "I heard something behind us,",
        "speaker": "Lina",
        "emotion": "fear",
        "voice_id": "pFZP5JQG7iQjIQuC4Bku"
    },
    {
        "idx": 3,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "Lina whispered. Sara looked around nervously and asked,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 4,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "Do you think someone is there?",
        "speaker": "Sara",
        "emotion": "fear",
        "voice_id": "cgSgspJ2msm6clMCkdW9"
    },
    {
        "idx": 5,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "Omar laughed and said,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 6,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "It is probably just a cat hiding in the bushes.",
        "speaker": "Omar",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "voice_id": "onwK4e9ZLuTAKqWW03F9"
    },
    {
        "idx": 7,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "A loud crash came from the alley beside them. Lina stepped back and cried,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 8,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "That was not a cat!",
        "speaker": "Lina",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "voice_id": "pFZP5JQG7iQjIQuC4Bku"
    },
    {
        "idx": 9,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "Ali took a deep breath and said,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 10,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "Stay close. We should check together.",
        "speaker": "Ali",
        "emotion": "joy",
        "voice_id": "CwhRBWXzGAHq8TQ4Fs17"
    },
    {
        "idx": 11,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "They moved slowly toward the alley. A small box had fallen from a wall, and inside it was a frightened kitten shaking in the cold. Sara smiled with relief and said,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 12,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "Oh no, it was just this little kitten.",
        "speaker": "Sara",
        "emotion": "joy",
        "voice_id": "cgSgspJ2msm6clMCkdW9"
    },
    {
        "idx": 13,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "Omar picked it up gently and said,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 14,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "I think we scared it more than it scared us.",
        "speaker": "Omar",
        "emotion": "fear",
        "voice_id": "onwK4e9ZLuTAKqWW03F9"
    },
    {
        "idx": 15,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "Lina laughed softly and said,",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    },
    {
        "idx": 16,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "text": "I was terrified for nothing.",
        "speaker": "Lina",
        "emotion": "fear",
        "voice_id": "pFZP5JQG7iQjIQuC4Bku"
    },
    {
        "idx": 17,
        "type": "narration",
        "text": "The four friends looked at one another and began to laugh as they carried the kitten home.",
        "speaker": null,
        "emotion": null,
        "voice_id": "JBFqnCBsd6RMkjVDRZzb"
    }
]